---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Bulk Grape Seed Extract Supplier | 95% OPC Proanthocyanidins | Weiyijie Bio"
  description="High-quality bulk grape seed extract supplier. 95% proanthocyanidins (OPC), water soluble, food/cosmetic grade, complete certifications, 1kg MOQ, fast global delivery."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bulk Grape Seed Extract</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">High-quality grape seed extract with 95% proanthocyanidins (OPC) for dietary supplements, cosmetics, and functional food. Water soluble, complete certifications, 1kg MOQ.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Product Specifications</h2>
            <table class="w-full">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Product Name</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Grape Seed Extract (Vitis Vinifera Extract)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Active Ingredient</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Proanthocyanidins (OPC, Procyanidins)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Purity</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">95% OPC (UV tested), 85% Polyphenols</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Appearance</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Reddish brown fine powder</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">CAS Number</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">84929-27-1</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Solubility</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Water soluble (100mg/ml clear solution)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Particle Size</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">100% pass 80 mesh</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-200">
                <td class="py-3 font-medium text-gray-900">Grade</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-gray-600">Food Grade / Cosmetic Grade available</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Key Health Benefits</h2>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">⚡</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Powerful antioxidant:</strong> 20x stronger than vitamin C, 50x stronger than vitamin E, neutralizes free radicals, reduces oxidative stress</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">❤️</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Cardiovascular health:</strong> Improves blood circulation, strengthens blood vessels, reduces LDL cholesterol, supports heart health</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">✨</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Skin health:</strong> Protects collagen and elastin from degradation, reduces wrinkles, improves skin elasticity, brightens skin tone</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🧠</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Cognitive function:</strong> Improves blood flow to the brain, supports memory and cognitive performance, reduces age-related cognitive decline</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🩹</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Anti-inflammatory:</strong> Reduces inflammation in the body, relieves joint pain, speeds up recovery from injury</span>
            </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Applications</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">💊</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Dietary Supplements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Capsules, tablets, softgels, powder blends for antioxidant and cardiovascular support. Recommended dosage: 100-300mg daily.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🥤</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Functional Beverages</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Health drinks, sports drinks, antioxidant waters, juice blends. Water soluble, no sediment, stable in low pH conditions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🧴</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cosmetics & Skincare</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Anti-aging serums, moisturizers, sun care products, brightening treatments. Protects skin from UV damage and premature aging.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🍬</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Functional Food</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Nutrition bars, confectionery, baked goods, instant drink mixes. Stable during processing and shelf life.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🐎</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Animal Nutrition</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Pet supplements, equine nutrition, livestock feed additives for antioxidant support.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center">
            <span class="text-3xl mb-3 block">🌿</span>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Natural Preservative</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Natural antioxidant for food and cosmetic products, extends shelf life without synthetic preservatives.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Packaging & Pricing</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Packaging Options</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📦</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>1kg/aluminum foil bag, vacuum sealed, food grade</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">📦</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>25kg/fiber drum, double plastic bag inside, lined with food grade PE bag</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">🎁</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>Custom packaging available (private label, custom sizes, printing logo)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Bulk Pricing (FOB China, Food Grade 95% OPC)</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>1-10kg: $35/kg</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>10-100kg: $30/kg</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-green-500 mt-1 text-xl">💰</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700>100kg+: $25/kg</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2">Discounts available for 500kg+ orders. Contact us for latest pricing and custom specification requests.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-green-200 mt-12">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-green-800 mb-4">Why Buy Grape Seed Extract from Weiyijie Bio?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">High quality grapes sourced from premium vineyards in Xinjiang, China, no pesticides or heavy metals</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Cold extraction process preserves active ingredients, high OPC content (95% minimum tested)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">100% water soluble, no fillers, no additives, non-GMO, gluten free</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Complete certifications: COA, SDS, TDS, FDA/REACH compliant, Kosher/Halal/Organic certified</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">1kg MOQ, sample orders available for quality testing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-600 mt-1">✅</span>
            <span class="text-gray-700">Fast delivery: 3-5 days for stock, 7-15 days global shipping with DHL/FedEx/UPS</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="text-center">
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all mr-4">
            Request Free Sample
          </a>
          <a href="/#contact" class="bg-white border-2 border-green-600 hover:bg-green-50 text-green-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all">
            Get Bulk Quote Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
